---
import LiveLedger from './LiveLedger.jsx';
---

<main class="animate-[fadeIn_0.4s_ease-out] bg-white min-h-screen pb-24">
  {/* Header */}
  <div class="bg-espresso text-cloud pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-butter font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4">Radical Transparency</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-heading font-black mb-6">The Glass Box</h1>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-80 max-w-2xl">
        <strong class="text-teal-600">Bottom Line Up Front:</strong> P31 Labs operates at zero cost to families. We don't hide our numbers because there's nothing to hide. Every dollar, every line of code, every decision is public.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 -mt-10">
    {/* Top Level Stats */}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-cloud">
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-espresso/50 uppercase mb-2">Revenue to Date</div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-black text-teal-600">$0</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-espresso/50 mt-4">Pre-revenue. All development is volunteer labor.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-cloud">
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-espresso/50 uppercase mb-2">Operating Expenses</div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-black text-espresso">$0<span class="text-lg opacity-50">/mo</span></div>
        <div class="text-sm text-espresso/50 mt-4">Cloudflare free tier. No paid services.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-cloud">
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-espresso/50 uppercase mb-2">Fiscal Sponsor</div>
        <div class="text-xl font-heading font-black text-coral-500">Hack Club (HCB)</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-espresso/50 mt-4">The Hack Foundation · EIN 81-2908499</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* How We Operate */}
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-espresso mb-6">How P31 Labs Operates at $0</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-cloud/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="font-bold text-espresso mb-2">Hosting</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-espresso/70">Cloudflare Pages (free tier) — static site hosting for phosphorus31.org, p31ca.org, and bonding.p31ca.org. Auto-SSL, global CDN.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cloud/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="font-bold text-espresso mb-2">Multiplayer Relay</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-espresso/70">Cloudflare Workers + KV (free tier) — 100K reads/day, 1K writes/day. Sufficient for BONDING's bulletin-board multiplayer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cloud/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="font-bold text-espresso mb-2">Development</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-espresso/70">100% volunteer. TypeScript, React, Three.js. 440+ automated tests. Zero paid dependencies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cloud/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="font-bold text-espresso mb-2">Source Code</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-espresso/70">GitHub (free). All repositories public under MIT license. Anyone can audit, fork, or contribute.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Transaction Ledger */}
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-espresso mb-2">Transaction Ledger</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-espresso/50 mb-6">
        Estimated data — live HCB ledger integration planned Q2 2026. All figures will link to Hack Club Bank public records.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-cloud overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <LiveLedger client:load />
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Public Roadmap */}
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-espresso mb-6">Public Roadmap</h3>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <span class="bg-teal-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">SHIPPED</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-espresso">BONDING v1.0</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-espresso/60">Multiplayer chemistry game — 11 elements, 82 molecules, 5 quest chains</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <span class="bg-teal-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">SHIPPED</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-espresso">Spaceship Earth v0.9</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-espresso/60">9-room cognitive dashboard — observatory, buffer, bridge, resonance, forge</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <span class="bg-butter text-espresso text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">IN PROGRESS</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-espresso">phosphorus31.org Overhaul</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-espresso/60">Warm Tech Humanity design, court readiness, Glass Box transparency</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <span class="bg-espresso/10 text-espresso text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">PLANNED</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-espresso">The Buffer (standalone)</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-espresso/60">Communication shield as independent tool for high-conflict co-parenting</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <span class="bg-espresso/10 text-espresso text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">PLANNED</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-espresso">Node One Hardware</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-espresso/60">ESP32-based biometric bridge for real-time stress detection</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Governance Documents */}
    <div class="bg-cloud/50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-espresso mb-4">Governance Documents</h3>
      <p class="text-espresso/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl">As a fiscally sponsored project under The Hack Foundation (501(c)(3)), we are building toward full independent nonprofit status.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="text-teal-600">📄</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-sm text-espresso">IRS Determination Letter</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-espresso/50">Via Hack Foundation</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="text-espresso/40">📄</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-sm text-espresso/60">Form 990</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-espresso/50">In preparation (Q2 2026)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="text-espresso/40">📄</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-sm text-espresso/60">Bylaws</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-espresso/50">In preparation</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="text-espresso/40">📄</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-sm text-espresso/60">Annual Report</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-espresso/50">Q2 2026</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="text-teal-600">📄</div>
          <div>
            <a href="https://github.com/p31labs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-bold text-sm text-teal-600 hover:underline">Open Source Licenses</a>
            <div class="text-xs text-espresso/50">MIT — all repositories</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-cloud">
          <div class="text-espresso/40">📄</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-sm text-espresso/60">Conflict of Interest Policy</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-espresso/50">In preparation</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
